Here I used the functional interface `Function&lt;A,B&gt;`, but there are many others in the package `java.util.function`. Most notable ones are

 - `Supplier`: `void -&gt; A`
 - `Consumer`: `A -&gt; void`
 - `BiConsumer`: `(A,B) -&gt; void`
 - `Function`: `A -&gt; B`
